com.kuka.mastering.provider.algorithms.mmd

Class MasteringAlgorithmMmd

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kuka.mastering.provider.algorithms.AbstractMasteringAlgorithm
      • com.kuka.mastering.provider.algorithms.mmd.MasteringAlgorithmMmd
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMasteringAlgorithm

    public class MasteringAlgorithmMmd
extends AbstractMasteringAlgorithm
    This class contains methods to automatically master the joints of a robot. The robot must be capable of reporting sensor queries for joint mastering (e.g. KUKA LBR iiwa).
    This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.

        masteringHelper - The algorithm helper which redirects the calls to the robot.
        preMasteringPositionFinder - The algorithm for searching the pre-mastering position.
        config - Algorithm configuration.
